    {
      "text": "Sports Illustrated: Championship Football & Baseball (known in Europe as All-American Championship Football) is a multiplatform sports video game that is licensed by sports magazine Sports Illustrated which features both American football and baseball games.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "Sports Illustrated: Championship Football & Baseball (conosciuto in  Europa come All-American Championship Football) è un videogioco commissionato dalla rivista Sports Illustrated, sviluppato da Malibu Games per Super Nintendo Entertainment System e include sia football americano sia baseball.",
      "lang": "it",
      "source": "wikipedia_it"
    },
    {
      "text": "『Sports Illustrated: Championship Football & Baseball』（ヨーロッパではAll-American Championship Footballとして知られる）は、スポーツ雑誌『Sports Illustrated』がライセンス提供する、アメリカンフットボールと野球の両方のゲームを収録したマルチプラットフォームのスポーツビデオゲームです。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "ai_local_gemma4",
      "base_lang": "en"
    }
  ]
